					<p class="show-more">Show More</p>
					<p class="hidden-description">To go skiing... just go outside! <br>The accommodation is particularly attractive to families and friends looking for a practical and comfortable chalet. During the day, adults can go skiing straight away while the kids are at the Panda-Club, the kids ski school,  which is only 300m from the chalet.</p>
