					<p class="hidden-description">Enjoy evenings in the hot-tub, the outdoor sauna or a summer barbecue on the terrace facing Les Grands-Montets.</p>
					<p class="hidden-description">For the children, there is a play-room upstairs which can also be used as an extra-bedroom for 2 kids under 6 years old.</p>
					<p class="hidden-description">In total, you can enjoy 2 double bedrooms, one bedroom with 2 single beds and a bunk-beds, 1 bedroom with 3 beds. All the beds (except the bunk beds) can be make as simple or double. Each bedroom has its own bathroom.</p>
